OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy for most with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain or showers, possibly
OL,7,Fheavy and thundery, especially over
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland. Driest in eastern
OL,9,FEngland with warm spells of sunshine
OL,10,Fhere until later with rain soon
OL,11,Farriving from the south.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA wet end to the day in the
OL,14,Fsouth with outbreaks of rain, locally
OL,15,Fheavy, pushing across England and
OL,16,FWales. Cloudy for Scotland with
OL,17,Fshowers in Northern Ireland slowly
OL,18,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
