OL,5,CSunday:FPersistent rain pushing
OL,6,Fnorthwards, mainly lingering in
OL,7,Fnorthern England. Sunshine and
OL,8,Fshowers, locally heavy, breaking out
OL,9,Fin the south with the driest
OL,10,Fconditions across Scotland.
